import { GoogleRecaptchaSection, SectionTitle, SectionForm } from './style';

const Home = () => (
    <GoogleRecaptchaSection>
        <SectionTitle>Google Recaptcha</SectionTitle>

        <SectionForm>
            <fieldset className="form__fieldset">
                <label className="fieldset__label">Type your name:</label>

                <input title="name" id="name" className="fieldset__name" />
            </fieldset>

            <fieldset className="form__fieldset">
                <button title="confirm" id="confirm" className="fieldset__button" type="submit">Confirm</button>
            </fieldset>
        </SectionForm>
    </GoogleRecaptchaSection>
)

export default Home
